  * ci(deny.toml): allow GPL and other OSI/FSF-free licenses ✅
  * ci(security): show offending license details in PR summary 📜
  * ci(deny.toml): migrate to cargo-deny ≥0.18 config; explicitly allow GPL/LGPL/MPL/EPL
  * ci(deny.toml): allow Zlib and Unicode-3.0 to satisfy cargo-deny
  * ci(codeql): auto-fix Cargo.lock in CI ✨🔒
