chd2iso-fuse (0.2.8-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  [ lloydsmart ]
  * chore(release): update CHANGELOG.md, debian/changelog, and Cargo.toml for v0.2.5
  * chore(release): update CHANGELOG.md, debian/changelog, and Cargo.toml for v0.2.6

  [ dependabot[bot] ]
  * chore(deps): bump actions/checkout from 4 to 5

  [ dependabot[bot] ]
  * chore(deps): bump actions/github-script from 7 to 8

  [ dependabot[bot] ]
  * chore(deps): bump actions/download-artifact from 4 to 5
  * ci: removed old workflows
  * ci: add unified CI workflow for PRs and pushes
  * ci: add release workflow triggered by tags
  * ci: auto-bump version and changelogs on release/* pushes
  * ci: rename release prep workflow to autobump.yml
  * ci: auto-create annotated tag on release/hotfix PR merge to main
  * ci: guard releases — only run when tag target is contained in main
  * ci: auto-open back-merge PR (main → develop) after release/hotfix merge
  * ci: combine auto-tag and back-merge into single on-merge workflow
  * docs: add developer runbook for release process
  * fix(workflows): clean up release.yml to resolve YAML parse error
  * fix(workflows): repair merge.yml syntax and simplify outputs
  * fix(workflows): sanitize merge.yml to resolve YAML parse error
  * fix(workflows): clean up merge.yml to resolve YAML parse error
  * fix(workflows): harden merge.yml back-merge logic and resolve YAML error
  * fix(workflows): quote job/step names in release.yml to resolve YAML error
  * fix(workflows): repair reusable build/verify workflows for merge/release
  * fix(workflows): pin reusable workflow calls in release/merge to branch ref
  * fix(workflows): sanitize release.yml artifact/download block and pin reusables
  * fix(workflows): sanitize release.yml around artifact download block
  * fix(workflows): harden release.yml around artifact download block
  * fix(workflows): quote wildcard pattern in release.yml
  * fix(workflows): make release.yml parser-proof and pin reusable refs
  * fix(workflows): simplify artifact download in release.yml to avoid YAML issues
  * ci(workflows): another fix?
  * ci(workflows): force-normalize line endings, remove non-UTF8 bytes, replace tabs with spaces
  * debian/watch: switch to git refs backend for robustness
  * ci: install gbp & Debian helpers for changelog step
  * ci(autobump): set DEBEMAIL/DEBFULLNAME for dch; keep gbp install
  * ci(autobump): install git-cliff (with cargo fallback) and libdistro-info-perl

  [ Lloyd Smart ]
  * chore(release): prepare v0.2.8 [skip ci]

  [ lloydsmart ]
  * ci(autobump): make changelog & notes deterministic (prev..HEAD)

  [ Lloyd Smart ]
  * chore(release): prepare v0.2.8 [skip ci]
  * chore(release): prepare v0.2.8 [skip ci]

  [ lloydsmart ]
  * ci(codeql): fail early when Cargo.lock is stale

 -- Lloyd Smart <lloydsmart@users.noreply.github.com>  Thu, 11 Sep 2025 10:23:07 +0000

